OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781000202
OL,3,CSomali referee denied entry to US for
OL,4,CWorld Cup
OL,6,FA Somali referee, who was due to
OL,7,Fofficiate in the 2026 World Cup, has
OL,8,Fbeen denied entry to the United States.
OL,10,FOmar Artan, who was set to become the
OL,11,Ffirst Somali to referee a World Cup
OL,12,Fmatch, was stopped at Miami
OL,13,FInternational Airport after arriving
OL,14,Ffrom Istanbul on Saturday.
OL,16,FFollowing an inspection, he was denied
OL,17,Fentry to the country due to "vetting
OL,18,Fconcerns", the US Customs and Border
OL,19,FProtection (CBP) said in a statement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
