OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781000202
OL,3,CSomali referee denied entry to US for
OL,4,CWorld Cup
OL,6,FThe CBP did not reference Artan by
OL,7,Fname, but he is the only Somali
OL,8,Freferee taking part in the World Cup.
OL,10,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FFifa confirmed on Monday that Artan
OL,16,Fwould not be able to train and
OL,17,Fofficiate at the tournament, which
OL,18,Fstarts across the US, Mexico and
OL,19,FCanada on June 11, with the majority
OL,20,Fof the games in the States.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781000202
OL,3,CSomali referee denied entry to US for
OL,4,CWorld Cup
OL,6,F"Despite the circumstances, I am in a
OL,7,Fpositive mood and I am focused on the
OL,8,Fnext challenges in my refereeing
OL,9,Fcareer," Artan, who was named the
OL,10,FConfederation of African Football's
OL,11,Freferee of the year in 2025, said in a
OL,12,Fstatement.
OL,14,F"I would like to thank Fifa and the
OL,15,FConfederation of African Football for
OL,16,Fall their support and I promise to
OL,17,Fkeep my refereeing levels up as I
OL,18,Fconcentrate on the future.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781000202
OL,3,CSomali referee denied entry to US for
OL,4,CWorld Cup
OL,6,F"I want to thank the football family
OL,7,Ffor their messages and wish my
OL,8,Fcolleagues all the best success during
OL,9,Fthe World Cup and I look forward to
OL,10,Fjoining them again in future
OL,11,Fcompetitions."
OL,13,FIn its own statement, Fifa said it was
OL,14,Fnot involved in the immigration
OL,15,Fprocesses and was informed by
OL,16,Fauthorities that Artan's status "will
OL,17,Fnot be changed at present".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
