CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781000202
OL,3,CSomali referee denied entry to US for
OL,4,CWorld Cup
OL,6,F"In line with previous Fifa events, a
OL,7,Fhost government ultimately determines
OL,8,Fwho receives a visa and who is
OL,9,Fadmitted into their country," the
OL,10,Ffootball association said.
OL,12,FTrump suspended the entry of Somali
OL,13,Fnationals in a proclamation June 2025,
OL,14,Fdescribing the country as a "terrorist
OL,15,Fsafe haven".
OL,17,FIt followed a January executive order
OL,18,Fwhich called on the administration
OL,19,Freport which countries had "deficient"
OL,20,Fvetting and screening information amid
OL,21,Fa crack down on immigration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
