PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781000202
OL,3,CSomali referee denied entry to US for
OL,4,CWorld Cup
OL,6,FThe entry of people from Afghanistan,
OL,7,FBurma, Chad, Republic of the Congo,
OL,8,FEquatorial Guinea, Eritrea, Haiti,
OL,9,FIran, Libya, Sudan, and Yemen is also
OL,10,Fsuspended.
OL,12,FIn its statement, the CBP said all
OL,13,Ftravellers entering the US are subject
OL,14,Fto a vetting process.
OL,16,F"During processing, the traveler
OL,17,Funderwent additional inspection, a
OL,18,Froutine part of CBP's inspection
OL,19,Fprocess when officers need to verify
OL,20,Finformation or determine
OL,21,Fadmissibility," it said.
OL,26,@}D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781000202
OL,3,CSomali referee denied entry to US for
OL,4,CWorld Cup
OL,6,F"Following inspection, the traveler, a
OL,7,Freferee for the FIFA World Cup, was
OL,8,Fdetermined to be inadmissible due to
OL,9,Fvetting concerns and was denied entry.
OL,11,F"Admissibility determinations are made
OL,12,Fon a case-by-case basis using law
OL,13,Fenforcement, national security, and
OL,14,Fimmigration information available at
OL,15,Fthe time of inspection," the statement
OL,16,Fcontinued.
OL,18,F"CBP officers have the authority to
OL,19,Fquestion travelers, conduct
OL,20,Finspections, and determine
OL,21,Fadmissibility consistent with US law."
